title: James Harden Triple-Double in His Brooklyn Nets debut
author: Brooklyn Nets
description: Brooklyn Nets guard James Harden becomes the first player in NBA history with a 30-point triple-double in his debut with a new team.

localize.description: 布鲁克林篮网队后卫詹姆斯-哈登成为NBA历史上第一位在新球队的首秀中拿到30分三双的球员。

localize.description: 布魯克林籃網隊後衛詹姆斯-哈登成爲NBA歷史上第一位在新球隊的首秀中拿到30分三雙的球員。
